Function (2) will remain positive for x < (b j2c). Consequently, within this
range of x, the quadratic function will exhibit increasing risk aversion, and
for values of x > (b j2c), the function will exhibit decreasing risk aversion.
The exponential utility function (EUF) can be represented as:
U = K-

